{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14328/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14328"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:43:28"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman walks down the stairs in a purple gown."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14328","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14328"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/canvas/1/81b44948-5657-4b70-aa5b-11c62d618ff1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-03T00:02:13.536Z","creator":"j","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma’s choice to wear the first dress he made for her is clearly intentional. Whether it is an attempt to reach out to him, reminding him of the happiness of their early relationship, or a dig, showing him that she can and will wear the dress for other people, without him, and that she does not need his company or kindness, is left unclear.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:889.5844944267512,77.28105095541395,590.7862261146497,975.7001393312102"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/canvas/1/956da16f-e910-433d-8b61-a62e26a13cbb","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-03T00:02:27.620Z","creator":"j","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Before Alma reappears wearing the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW86087641 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-03249.html\"><u>first dress</u></a> Reynolds made for her, Reynolds’s leg can be seen sticking out from the table. His <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW86087641 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-00145.html\"><u>pink sock</u></a> matches Alma’s dress.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14328/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1540.9917396496812,721.0300557324839,112.46865047770711,282.85778264331213"}}}]}]}]}